{"tid":1502411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手檢舉CCTV用廣東話係Youtube落廣告誤導大眾帶風向","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T03:09:04.000Z","uid":291545,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b38c5f90224b56bf53d7ebe8dfa708c7bd801c21","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:08:39.000Z","msg":"唔知有無手足po過<br />\n啱啱用youtube睇片見到CCTV買晒廣告扮到成個蘋果咁，一定呃到一班無腦嘅豬<br />\n有用過youtube都知youtube無比錢就一定要睇佢哋廣告先入到正題，咁樣迫人睇CCTV廣告洗人腦帶風向，抹黑170萬人上街嘅民意事實真係極度賤<br />\n原來條片21／8已經出咗街<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">懇求大家一齊舉報佢個垃圾廣告！！！！！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mDMU7Be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmDMU7Be.png&h=2b5563ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiaOsD5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiaOsD5.jpg&h=5dc6c598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7ULuSq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7ULuSq.jpg&h=02b786d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5EY8sD6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5EY8sD6.jpg&h=34b04017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qLW9Wxr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqLW9Wxr.jpg&h=e0eb62b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉報方法：<br />\n舉報廣告的方法<br />\n步驟 1：確定是 Google 廣告<br />\n首先，請確定您要舉報的是 Google 廣告。以下列舉您可能會看到的不同 Google 廣告類型。<br />\n<br />\n「Google 搜尋」上的廣告：這類廣告會在「Google 搜尋結果網頁」及其他 Google 服務 (例如「Google 購物」) 上顯示。<br />\n非 Google 網站和應用程式上的廣告：Google 廣告可能會在非 Google 網站和應用程式上顯示。如果您看到 AdChoices 圖示 AdChoices icon 連同讓您忽略廣告的 [X] 圖示，就可視之為 Google 廣告。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">YouTube 上的廣告：這類廣告會顯示在 YouTube 影片底部或右側。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">步驟 2：舉報廣告<br />\n填妥「舉報廣告」表格。<br />\n<br />\n提交舉報表格後，您將會收到確認電郵。我們會檢視您的舉報內容，並在適當的情況下對有關廣告採取行動。</span></span><br />\n表格係呢度：<a href=\"https://support.google.com/google-ads/answer/7660847?hl=zh-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fgoogle-ads%2Fanswer%2F7660847%3Fhl%3Dzh-HK&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84pIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=60653816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/google-ads/answer/7660847?hl=zh-HK</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">OR</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2。YOUTUBE檢舉<br />\n<br />\n電腦：<br />\n登入 YouTube。<br />\n在要檢舉的影片的播放器下方點選「更多」圖示 更多。<br />\n在下拉式選單中選取 [檢舉]。<br />\n針對您要檢舉的影片，選擇一個最合適的違規理由。<br />\n提供額外細節 (包括影片中出現不當內容的時間戳記) 或說明違規原因，協助 YouTube 審查小組進一步瞭解影片實際情況，進而做出公正的決定。<br />\n<br />\nAndroid和Apple：<br />\n前往您要檢舉的影片的觀賞頁面。<br />\n輕觸影片頂端的「更多」圖示 。<br />\n輕觸「檢舉」圖示 。<br />\n選擇一個檢舉理由。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/2802027?hl=zh-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fyoutube%2Fanswer%2F2802027%3Fhl%3Dzh-HK&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84pIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=d845a907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/2802027?hl=zh-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其他檢舉方式<br />\n如果檢舉程序無法確切反映您的問題，我們還有其他許多回報機制可供您使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n檢舉工具<br />\n如要回報違反《社群規範》的影片，檢舉影片是您可以採用的好辦法，但有時您可能需要回報多則內容，或是希望回報更詳細的資訊以供我們審查。您可以使用檢舉工具，醒目顯示使用者的評論與影片，並提供其他資訊。如果您認為自己成為騷擾/濫用行為的目標，我們也建議您透過這項工具來檢舉內容。<br />\n透過 YouTube 內建的檢舉工具<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/reportabuse\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Freportabuse&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84pIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=af2cec34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/reportabuse</a>來檢舉騷擾/濫用行為。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n內容自己諗啦，例如抹黑，散播假消息之類，講埋CCTV係中共喉舌嚟，係Youtube最近封嘅Ac其中一份子要求封埋佢等等<br />\n揀選項果啲： 對弱勢族群發表仇恨言論&amp;垃圾內容與詐騙"},{"pid":"f72c51e813360b1e872322333ee0ff63a9faa71f","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"594b211e21c2225767eda0cf0b35d3787724be62","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"5fb8092fd1b5abe9c6533799365115303c3de127","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3486edb0192ea804e362349ed51d1b2b6d4e9c0","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fbac4f82d7e5c5f494b33d5bc77e3e4e71c0c9e","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e5ddc2ac67733206287bb001e3d78a0a69727c5","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:12:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10439c74e5127893e4f5154e60a69dd0611f38e6","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"013246ae36bfbecfde8587fca0cde3a7feff1f17","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa2442d818568c49fc6546eb10569d2372e7236e","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:14:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3783f3ca48d8555936b63d580b3bdf0889c983d","tid":1502411,"uid":85965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇到都想屌<br />\n明明係cctv channel但唯獨係呢條片廣東話<br />\n講d唔講d之餘最後仲要屌哂其他記者<br />\n明顯係想屈人數加要人質疑記者<br />\n用心極之惡毒"},{"pid":"d8a9f95dac62786e18aae48f21a807551a7f0895","tid":1502411,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid"