sg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/english/features/june4/headcount/2009/5_Dr.So_June4_Headcount_Area+Calculation_2009.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkupop.hku.hk%2Fenglish%2Ffeatures%2Fjune4%2Fheadcount%2F2009%2F5_Dr.So_June4_Headcount_Area%2BCalculation_2009.pdf&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84pIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=2df6d6d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/english/features/june4/headcount/2009/5_Dr.So_June4_Headcount_Area+Calculation_2009.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ETWNJFr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETWNJFr.png&h=22b282de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HA6J1sg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHA6J1sg.png&h=611a7014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以HKU Pop 每平方米 2.8 人計算:2.8 人/米 x 43293 平方米 = 121220 人。 <br />\n以HKU Pop 每平方米 2.5 人計算:2.5 人/米 x 43293 平方米 = 108233 人。<br />\n以港鐡標準 每平方米 6人計算:6 人/米 x 43293 平方米 = 259758 人<br />\n以港鐵下限 每平方米 4人計算:4 人/米 x 43293 平方米 = 173172 人<br />\n<br />\n我點計都唔會係6萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277ea02806e0518fdf74e1b0f3a9ce6238a369b5","tid":1502411,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"926520a7ba4da5c8bc8ff873c5a8fa3687199483","tid":1502411,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e473e43116a4ff909a413df569f1b0f9fae72f2","tid":1502411,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"條廣告既網址係咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XALoQgIKe-U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXALoQgIKe-U&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84pIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=0dbd9d10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XALoQgIKe-U</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"條片PRIVATE左, 睇唔到了"}]}